Base words: (1) SOCIETY, (2) PROBLEM, (3) SOLVE, (4) COHESIVE, (5) ISSUE', '{"prompt_es":"Fill in the gaps with the correct form of the word provided in parentheses.\n\nBase words: (1) SOCIETY, (2) PROBLEM, (3) SOLVE, (4) COHESIVE, (5) ISSUE","mastery_tag":"vocabulary:b2-society","main_text":"In modern (1)___, many people face various social (2)___. Governments often work towards finding (3)___ to these issues, promoting (4)___ within communities. It is important to raise awareness about social (5)___ and work together for positive change.","correct_answer":["SOCIETY","PROBLEMS","SOLUTIONS","COHESION","ISSUES"],"explanation":"(1) undefined\n(2) undefined\n(3) undefined\n(4) undefined\n(5) undefined","complexity":3,"concept_tags":["vocabulary","society","unit"]}')
